      "text": "saucer sightings since August 1952. We have a State",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Representative in most of the 50 states, and in seven",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "foreign countries. We have a Scientific Panel of known",
      "status": "image_matched"
