      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the Air Force files on their saucer investigation since",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "1948. Among the sightings we are interested in is one",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "recent one, Soccorro, New Mexico, April 25, 1964. This",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
